## Join the two tables innear join used to join

link to practice that question : https://livesql.oracle.com/apex/livesql/s/nyc4oidddn8tajab5zq3qfflr

Table_name1 : table1

colA
Null
1
5
2
1
Null

Table_name2 : table2

colB
2
null
5
5

Required output:
COLA	COLB
 -	   -
 5    5
 5   	5
 2   	2
 -   	-
 
 Soultion:
 select *from table1 inner join table2 
on table1.colA=table2.colB or (table1.colA is null and table2.colB is null);



